ticular YTPMVs easier to find and discover;\nUse shorter clips. 10 seconds should do it. Don't wanna spoil too much of the video for someone who's never seen it.\nPut the titles under the video while it's playing. That way when someone skips ahead and stumble upon one they like, they immediately know the name and don't have to search for it.","like_count":3,"author_id":"UC7qOa0JgA40mPndZfzl6MiA","author":"@TheWazzz","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_kPjx_mQa1VovEpWb7XqPc_ml7YvGfiZIIZBgxVfVcA92g=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@TheWazzz","is_favorited":false,"timestamp":1556409600,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"UgxNLH_4sixBsju5sTV4AaABAg.8qVF29e524Y8qVIUUWLyZI","parent":"UgxNLH_4sixBsju5sTV4AaABAg","text":"Well, I'd rather cut small enough segments that they get enough exposure, but that they don't get cut off in middle of a melody or something like that. Though in case of your video, I ended up featuring almost all of it since I think it was just that good and I couldn't think of which part to highlight. And to be fair, even if I haven't featured the name of the video as it's being played, I have named each of them and their authors right before they start to play and I have all of the videos linked in the playlist in the description. But yeah, that's a pretty fair observation and note to make, I'll try to keep that in mind for future reference, or at the very least not expose as much of each video in my future compilations","like_count":2,"author_id":"UCwiGSPpRzQkw80OKDeN8Wvw","author":"@FinnOtaku","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_nNsIn_qk_ULwmmn7XM9pL6v_Rm_z5xiQ_a8zw3TdU8gUA=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":true,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@FinnOtaku","is_favorited":false,"timestamp":1556409600,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"UgymjDGXoteInt2sYpx4AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"It's only to be expected from you but this is the best compilation","like_count